message.body: Whoooaaa. I want to check it out. Wtf is going on in the first one
I don't know. I think it might just be malnourished oysters but it looks like coral
Are u working? I got some stuff for u if you wanna come over and check out the logs
I am working but i can stop by later...will you be around after 7?
Yeah I got a huge ganoderma for u and some dryads saddle if you want to try to clone it. Plus I found a bunch of oyster logs. Gotta go back with a hatchet or saw
Awesome. Tomorrow? I need a real gas powered chainy
Yeah that might raise some eyebrows in chamounix. I'm going on a long bike ride tomorrow but I could take u there in the morning
I've got homemade lemon chicken soup if you want
You home now? Im on yr porch
I had to leave as Im feeling ill. When are you leaving tomorrow to ride?

I'm not sure when I'm leaving. It's up to Lindsey but I'd say sometime between 11am and 1pm so we could hit it up in the morning if you want. I'd like to get the dryad and ganoderma to you before they spoil
Yeah lemmie swing by in the am or vice versa. Call ya when i wake
Hey man let me know if i should stop by. Making breakfast
I'm around til noon or so
I'm hopping in the shower so wait a few before u come
Cool still doing breakfast shoukd be over closer to 11
